content: Why I have to pay on another device with the same account???
replyContent: Thanks for your feedback. You can use apps you bought on Google Play on any Android device without paying again. However, each device must have the same Google Account on it. Please, read more here: https://bit.ly/2EJCYvP . If you have troubles or questions, please contact our support and we will help.

replyContent: Thank you for the review. To solve the problem with the quiz you can just turn on the option in the settings: "Exit test by holding down the "Back" button". You can find the settings by pressing the Language button at the app main screen.
